#. type: delimited block =
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access/r2dbc.adoc:130
msgid ""
"`DatabaseClient` provides the basic functionality of running a statement.  "
