#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access/r2dbc.adoc:222
msgid ""
"`one()` returns exactly one result and fails if the result contains more "
"rows.  Using Kotlin Coroutines, `awaitOne()` for exactly one value or "
"`awaitOneOrNull()` if the value may be `null`."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access/r2dbc.adoc:223
